astolfo.description: The cream of the crop, the best of the best. Astolfo is all you can ask for and more. And he is a paladin of justice. A true hero of his people, and protector of those that need it. His will is unwavering, his courage unyielding, his grace unmatched. Truly the best man there is.

malphasie.description: Malphasie is the best goth gf you can ask for. She a snacc, and she give snack. Her sprite is insanely attractive and cute. Plus hybrids are fun.

lovely_katy.description: Katy is a great singer, and quite lovely. Her lovely hair makes up for the otherwise, unlovely dress. But she's our superstar this year, and you can say her reign is *never really over*.

ai_katy_perry.description: AI Katy is the creepy ex girlfriend you tried to get rid of. But instead of moving on she murdered you. Make sure to run your anti-virus software.
